,Not Recommended,270880,28939396,Posted: 2 January,all,Bownsy105,"This is the second time I have purchased this game, and the second time I have requested a refund.As a fan of Euro Truck sim 2 I wanted to like this game. ETS2 was released back in 2012, and for a game that was brand new as of early 2016, I did not feel that enough had changed.Fast forward to now and I still feel the same. The graphics are not much of an improvement over ETS2. The progression and management systems are identical and overall nothing more has been done to the simulation aspect of this game.I feel this game could have been a great opportunity to build a modern truck sim from the ground up, and improve upon the problems that where apparent in ETS2. However, SCS, instead of improving the formula, have just copied ETS2 problems and all. If you have never purchased a truck sim from SCS before then this is not a bad buy, you will probably have fun. That said, if you’re coming over from ETS2 and looking for an improved experience, then I can't recommend this game, at least not in it's current state."
